        "title": "fix(memory): guard against missing agentIds in wiki artifact clone and sort",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n`cloneMemoryPublicArtifact` used `[...artifact.agentIds]` which crashes when `agentIds` is `undefined`. All `wiki_*` tools threw `artifact.agentIds is not iterable`.\n\n## Fix\n\n- `cloneMemoryPublicArtifact`: use `Array.isArray(artifact.agentIds) ? [...artifact.agentIds] : []`\n\n## Files changed\n- `src/plugins/memory-state.ts` — 1 line guard\n\nCloses #92207",
